You may obtain your access token by making a POST request with your credentials. To the right you'll find examples in many popular languages.

<br />

The authentication endpoint uses the following response/error codes:

<br />

Response code | Meaning
------------- | -------
200           | OK
401           | Invalid credentials
404           | Service not available
405           | Wrong method (i.e. GET instead of POST)
